Simple Substitution Cipher Setiap huruf diganti menggunakan alfabet acak. Tools dCode Substitution Cipher, 
Cryptii Substitution Cipher.
alphabet = "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ"
key      = "QWERTYUIOPASDFGHJKLZXCVBNM"

mapping = dict(zip(alphabet, key))

text = "HELLO"

cipher = ''.join(mapping[c] for c in text)

