XOR Cipher Operasi XOR antara plaintext dan key. Tools CyberChef, dCode XOR Cipher.
def xor_encrypt(text, key):
    result = ""

    for c in text:
        result += chr(ord(c) ^ key)

    return result

cipher = xor_encrypt("HELLO", 5)

print(cipher)
